                        sling:resourceType="core/franklin/components/block/v1/block/item"
                        aueComponentId="text-container-text"
                        model="text-container-text"
                        modelFields="[text@richtext]"
                        name="Text Container Text"
                        text="&lt;p>This means the AbbVie employee or third-party worker you are visiting has NOT preregistered you for guest Wi-Fi access.&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>1. On your device, go to &lt;strong>Wi-Fi settings&lt;/strong>.&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>2. Select &lt;strong>&lt;em>AbbVie-Guest&lt;/em>&lt;/strong>&lt;em>.&lt;/em>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>3. On the Guest Wi-Fi Login screen, select &lt;strong>Register for Guest Access&lt;/strong>.&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>4. Complete the Registration form and click &lt;strong>Register.&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;strong>5. An email&lt;/strong> will be sent to your sponsoring AbbVie employee or third-party worker, who must be onsite or on VPN to approve your access.&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>6. Once your sponsor approves your request, you will receive a &lt;strong>confirmation email&lt;/strong> with your login credentials. &lt;strong>Follow the steps&lt;/strong> listed under I’m Sponsored to access AbbVie’s guest Wi-Fi.&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;strong>Need assistance?&lt;/strong> Contact your AbbVie sponsoring employee/third-party worker.&lt;/p>"/>
