                        summary="How long does it take to get guest Wi-Fi access?"
                        text="&lt;p>Your access time depends on your sponsorship status.&lt;/p>&lt;p>If you’re already sponsored, you’ll have guest Wi-Fi access as soon as you enter your login credentials on &lt;em>AbbVie-Guest&lt;/em>. These are found in your sponsorship email.&lt;/p>&lt;p>If you’re not sponsored, you’ll need to submit your request to the person you’re visiting. Once they’ve approved your request, you’ll automatically receive your sponsorship email and can log in.&lt;/p>"/>
                    <item_7
